B.a7Q=new A.nu("The basics",null)
B.a80=new A.uQ("1","Drag a block","Blocks slide in straight lines only. A block keeps going until it bumps into another block or the wall.",null)
B.a8_=new A.uQ("2","Find its matching gate","Gates are the coloured bars around the edge of the board. A red block can only leave through a red gate.",null)
B.a81=new A.uQ("3","Push it out","Line the block up with its gate and drag it PAST the edge. Letting go at the edge just parks it \u2014 you have to push it through.",null)
B.a82=new A.uQ("4","Clear the board","When every movable block is gone, the level is done and the next one loads automatically.",null)
B.a7U=new A.nu("Blocks you will meet",null)
B.a7A=new A.eQ("Coloured blocks","The normal ones. Each has an emblem (\u25c6 \u25cf \u2b22 \u25b2) so you can tell them apart by shape as well as colour.",null)
B.a7H=new A.eQ("Steel blocks","Grey, with rivets. They NEVER move and have no gate. Route everything else around them.",null)
B.a7C=new A.eQ("Rail blocks","Marked with arrows. They slide on that one axis only \u2014 push them the other way and nothing happens.",null)
B.a7x=new A.eQ("Gems","The glowing diamonds. Slide any block over one to sweep it up. They are your currency.",null)
B.a7T=new A.nu("Scoring big",null)
B.a7N=new A.eQ("Chains","Clear blocks quickly one after another and the chain climbs. Every link is worth more than the last.",null)
B.a7D=new A.eQ("Streaks","Send the SAME colour out back-to-back for a feed bonus on top of the chain.",null)
B.a7B=new A.eQ("\ud83d\ude80 Rocket","Chain 7 in one run and a rocket sweeps every block left on the board. Rare, and worth chasing.",null)
B.a7z=new A.eQ("Board clear","Finishing on a big chain sets off the biggest celebration in the game.",null)
B.a7S=new A.nu("What is on screen",null)
B.a7M=new A.eQ("Top left","Score, current level, and your gems.",null)
B.a7y=new A.eQ("Pause \xb7 Help \xb7 Skip","Pause the run, ask the guide, or throw away this board and get a new one.",null)
B.a7E=new A.eQ("Bottom left","This run: levels cleared, best chain, gems and score.",null)
B.a7J=new A.eQ("Board edges","The coloured bars are the gates. A gate lights up when the block you are dragging can go through it.",null)
B.a7V=new A.nu("Make it yours",null)
B.a7L=new A.eQ("Soundtrack","Ten tracks \u2014 seven calm, three chaos. They all build as your chain climbs. Settings \u2192 Soundtrack.",null)
B.a7K=new A.eQ("Sound packs","Change the texture of every tap and slide. Settings \u2192 Sound packs.",null)
B.a7G=new A.eQ("ASMR mode","Softer, slower, warmer. Good for winding down.",null)
B.a7I=new A.eQ("Calm / Quiet","Turns off screen shake and freeze-frames. The game plays exactly the same, it just sits still.",null)
B.a7F=new A.eQ("Haptics","Vibration on every clear. Turn it off if you prefer.",null)
B.a7R=new A.nu("Tips",null)
B.a8a=new A.uR("Look for the blocks that can already leave \u2014 clearing those first opens lanes for the stuck ones.",null)
B.a89=new A.uR("A block only needs a clear path in ONE direction. Check both ways before deciding it is trapped.",null)
B.a88=new A.uR("Plan the whole chain before your first drag. Chains are timed, so hesitating breaks them.",null)
B.a87=new A.uR("Every board can always be solved. If you are stuck, something just needs to move out of the way first.",null)
B.aQ=new A.dO(null,24,null,null)
